reviewText: dont know its for my mom for x-mas

This video chronicles 12 months of a rescued Honey Badger's life.  It is extremely short, and suffers from a bad transfer to DVD.  The bottom fifth of the picture is obscured by scan line errors that can't catch the rest of the image.  If you're interested in the antics of Honey Badgers, then "Nature: Honey Badgers", found on Netflix, is a much better program.
A story of "Badgie" a orphan young Honey-Badger frome the view of a normal household.
